Language name: Iai
Language number: 2422
Alternate names: Iaai
Classification: Austro-Tai, E. Malayo-Polynesian
Comments: Iai is spoken in Ouvea Island, Loyality Islands 
in New Caledonia.

Sources: 

Haudricourt, A.G. 1971. New Caledonia and the Loyalty 
Islands. Current Trends in Linguistics (T. Sebeok ed.) 8: 
359-396.

Ozanne-Rivierre, F. 1976. Le Iaai. SELAF, Paris.

Tryon, D.T. 1968. Iai Grammar (Pacific Linguistics, Series 
B, 8). Australian National University, Canberra.